Hello everyone and thank you for helping us around.
So here is my question:

I am trying to develop an HTML+Hubl + Bootstrap5 template where i want the editor to be able to modify some sections (for example move content from col 1 to col 2 supposing that i have 2 columns), or move 1 section below the other.

My test code is that :
```&lt;!--
    templateType: page
    isAvailableForNewContent: true
--&gt;
<!DOCTYPE html>
&lt;html lang="en"&gt;

